This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image analysis and segmentation. The use of deep neural networks also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The mention of the 2018 MICCAI challenge suggests that it could also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of a novel loss function suggests that it could belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
